Yosemite National Park.title: Yosemite National Park
Yosemite National Park.byline: Yosemite National Park is a national park and a UNESCO World Heritage Site in the Sierra Nevada mountains in east-central California.
edges: Sequoia and Kings Canyon National Parks

Yosemite West.title: Yosemite West
Yosemite West.byline: Yosemite West is a small community in Mariposa County, California, is accessed via roads in Yosemite National Park.

Yoshino.title: Yoshino
Yoshino.byline: Yoshino (吉野) is a town in Nara Prefecture, Japan.

Yoshinogari.title: Yoshinogari
Yoshinogari.byline: Yoshinogari (吉野ヶ里町) is a town of 16,000 people (2017) in Saga Prefecture, Japan.

Yoshkar-Ola.title: Yoshkar-Ola
Yoshkar-Ola.byline: Yoshkar-Ola (Russian: Йошка́р-Ола́ yahsh-KAHR ah-LAH) is the capital of Mari El in the Volga Region of the Russian Federation.
